citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:40-2:10pm on 3
January 2022.
The inspector knocked on the door, left a message at the contact phone number, and waited 30 minutes before departing
the facility.
End Section
